description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Better Healthcare services supports adults and children with long term clinical, complex health and social care needs. Our specialist care team provide a high standard of care and support to people living in their own homes within the Norfolk community.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt; &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are recruiting for support workers to provide support to an elderly gentleman in his own home. Our client lives in Carbrooke and requires 24 hour care 7 days a week. He has dementia, communication needs and is at high risk of falling.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;The role will include: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Personal Care&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Social support  &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supporting with safety and mobility&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Light housework duties&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Successful candidates will be working waking night shifts 19:30 – 07:30, we currently have a full and part time role available.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; For this role a minimum of 3 months previous care experience is essential along with a caring nature, some experience with dementia would be beneficial. All successful applicants will be subject to a DBS check and satisfactory references. &lt;br /&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Come and be part of a great team!!! Apply today to receive:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;£10.00 - £11.00 per hour&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free training&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ongoing support and career development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Weekly pay&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Refer a friend bonus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Regular hours&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Paid Holiday&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;PPE and uniform provided&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
